
Overview of adv dearly

The adv dearly has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (2) dearly, in a heartfelt way -- (in a sincere and heartfelt manner; "I would dearly love to know")
2. (1) dearly, dear -- (at a great cost; "he paid dearly for the food"; "this cost him dear")
3. dearly, affectionately, dear -- (with affection; "she loved him dearly"; "he treats her affectionately")
